red;\">要檢討唔可以好似terry咁正面啲出個檢討post嘅咩？錯嘅係港共，而最愛香港嘅就係嗰班企到最前嗰班手足呀，罷工嘅手足就係勇武</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後大家一齊做好啲，至少係輿論上支援手足，做到更多就繼續去做<br />\n<br />\n好耐無係連登post見到口號啦，我哋一齊提醒返自己啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不指責，不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">齊上齊落，和勇不分</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立，唯一出路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同嘅就幫手推下，多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b500b3afb1a42ddc41300222533717ab2c86b0","tid":1870660,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"推~~~"},{"pid":"368f0571df2c1af601eac85fa92571f376cde247","tid":1870660,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦，連登發晦氣鬧人抵死垃圾就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5219745eb811003f926acf141c633c051ad29b","tid":1870660,"uid":194188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"同意 出檢討po 但第一樣唔屌高層政府厚顏無恥 係度屌醫護 雖然我都知有五毛"},{"pid":"c074f251c3b62103a0dbb92df7dde01a7fbf535a","tid":1870660,"uid":329288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f5219745eb811003f926acf141c633c051ad29b","tid":1870660,"uid":194188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"同意 出檢討po 但第一樣唔屌高層政府厚顏無恥 係度屌醫護 雖然我都知有五毛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"多謝支持，不過師兄你用左不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係連登出長文正經post真係TLDR，p牌又推唔到"},{"pid":"43355581cd6607aa41caf84af8351db4b7939f61","tid":1870660,"uid":175346,"like":1,"disl